Always focus on high performance, fast load times, and avoiding redundant or unused code/libraries.

If the project becomes too large for the AI context window, split it into independent modules (e.g., UI, Letters, Branch Management, etc.).

Large image/media files can be excluded from the AI context using the .bolt/ignore file.

Keep all modules documented, and provide a brief description for any new feature or section.

